### USAGE INSTRUCTIONS:
### 1. Make sure your Next.js development server is running: npm run dev
### 2. Install HTTPyac extension in VS Code or use any HTTP client
### 3. Click "Send Request" above any of the POST requests
### 4. The API will create both Firebase Auth account and Firestore user profile
### 5. Super admin will have all permissions and can access all dashboard features
###
### IMPORTANT NOTES:
### - Change passwords before using in production
### - Each email can only be used once
### - Super admin accounts are automatically approved and activated
### - Super admin accounts have full system permissions
### - Use strong passwords in production environment
###
